{"tid":851621,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【蝕住出貨】5年前買西環新地樓 今日輸360萬","createTime":"2018-10-07T09:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T23:08:16.000Z","uid":147097,"like":79,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"940d3359b4c10fdbb32d2c5cbd80d4c961280be9","tid":851621,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:47:29.000Z","msg":"新地（016）發展的西環卑路乍街Imperial Kennedy再錄蝕讓。<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，該廈高層A室，實用面積901方呎，3房間隔，上月21日登記以2,380萬元賣出，呎價26,415元。賣方2013年11月向新地以2,611.4萬元一手買入，持貨近5年賬面貶值231.4萬元或8.9%。若計及佣金及釐印費等開支，料蝕逾360萬元。<br />\n<br />\n區內代理表示，該單位早於去年5月已放盤，業主拒蝕讓，開價2,780萬元，最終減價400萬元終沽出。"},{"pid":"8cca1e50f288fb287bcdf5747f5124ed616305a7","tid":851621,"uid":162526,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:54:26.000Z","msg":"西環唔計"},{"pid":"2e311ee677ef2a7250d3c698bec3e7ac25965fb6","tid":851621,"uid":31744,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:56:46.000Z","msg":"又話一定賺嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30aa4b4ce2c0e9ef7db86cf507fab8f594694fc","tid":851621,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:58:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc72976a284972bd89a9658cc2352612b766b1fd","tid":851621,"uid":93321,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"2千幾萬唔計"},{"pid":"4780928426727a58b0a98a6f81705b50f3bc6469","tid":851621,"uid":165773,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:59:15.000Z","msg":"仲有排跌 接果個真係祝福佢：）"},{"pid":"6881a0afcb1a1547d75456d9daf202c6df908b5f","tid":851621,"uid":162526,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2e311ee677ef2a7250d3c698bec3e7ac25965fb6","tid":851621,"uid":31744,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:56:46.000Z","msg":"又話一定賺嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:59:34.000Z","msg":"假跌"},{"pid":"2